PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue designating Albania, Austria, the Azerbaijani Republic, Bulgaria, Finland, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Moldova, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia and the Republic of Uzbekistan as "designated states" for the purposes of this Act, and declaring that the Act, except Part VI, shall apply to them.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1999-0086 Publication Date: 1999-03-03
Attachments
precis:
Order directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue designating Albania, Austria,
the Azerbaijani Republic, Bulgaria, Finland, Georgia, Kazakhstan, Moldova,
Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia and
the Republic of Uzbekistan as "designated states" for the purposes of this
Act, and declaring that the Act, except Part VI, shall apply to them.
